public class ProcessVariableWithArchive
extends AbstractControlSystemItem
implements IProcessVariableWithArchive

Minimal IProcessVariableNameWithArchiveDataSource implementation.

The drag-and-drop transfer uses it internally.
Applications which need to provide IArchiveDataSource can use this, but can also implement the interface themselves.
